title: Pappa Rich
typeOfFood: Ovo, Juice bar, Take-out, Fusion, Malaysian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain restaurant, opens til late. Menu offers around 5 vegetarian dishes that can be requested vegan by omitting egg; plus there are a few veg sides like steamed buns and sticky rice. Most dishes are traditional Malay food that center around a satan mutton. Has soy milk (warm and cold) and fresh juices.
